<i>♪ We're not gonna
take it anymore ♪</i>

1075
00:55:13.655 --> 00:55:16.451
<i>♪ We're not gonna take it</i>

1076
00:55:17.037 --> 00:55:19.695
<i>♪ No. we ain't gonna take it</i>

1077
00:55:20.524 --> 00:55:25.563
<i>♪ We're not gonna
take it anymore ♪</i>

1078
